   611	
   612	## Algorithm — what the 3-trial experiment looks like across 5 processes
   613	
   614	```text
   615	harness
   616	  ├─> task-store-server (uvicorn, SqliteStore, shared_token=T)
   617	  │       bound to 127.0.0.1:$PORT after printing EDEN_TASK_STORE_LISTENING
   618	  ├─> planner-host  (StoreClient, ScriptedPlanner, worker-id=planner-1)
   619	  ├─> implementer-host (StoreClient, ScriptedImplementer, worker-id=implementer-1)
   620	  ├─> evaluator-host   (StoreClient, ScriptedEvaluator, worker-id=evaluator-1)
   621	  └─> orchestrator (StoreClient, Integrator, plan-tasks=plan-1,plan-2,plan-3)
   622	```
   623	
   624	1. Harness boots task-store-server, reads its port from stdout.
   625	2. Harness boots the 3 workers and orchestrator in parallel with the
   626	   URL and shared token. Each waits on readiness probe.
   627	3. Orchestrator seeds plan-1, plan-2, plan-3.
   628	4. Planner's next poll returns the 3 pending plan tasks. It claims
   629	   each, drafts `--proposals-per-plan` proposals (each carrying
   630	   `parent_commits=(base_commit_sha,)`), marks each ready, submits.
   631	5. Orchestrator's next iteration: finalizes plan tasks (accepts
   632	   each), dispatches an implement task per ready proposal.
   633	6. Implementer claims each, writes a real commit on
   634	   `refs/heads/work/<slug>-<trial_id>` in the shared bare repo via
   635	   `GitRepo`, creates a trial carrying that branch + SHA, and
   636	   submits `status=success`.
   637	7. Orchestrator accepts implement tasks, dispatches evaluate tasks.
   638	8. Evaluator claims each, submits metrics.
   639	9. Orchestrator accepts evaluate tasks (this also writes metrics on
   640	   the trial per the §2.2 composite commit). Trials are now
   641	   `success`.
   642	10. Orchestrator calls `Integrator.integrate(trial_id)` for each:
   643	    writes `refs/heads/trial/<id>-<slug>` via zero-oid CAS into the
   644	    bare repo, then `POST /trials/{id}/integrate` → store writes
   645	    `trial_commit_sha` + `trial.integrated` event.
   646	11. Next iteration finds no progress. Counter increments. After
   647	    `--max-quiescent-iterations` zero-progress iterations in a row,
   648	    orchestrator exits 0.
   649	12. Harness observes the exit, asserts DB + repo state, SIGTERMs the
   650	    workers + task-store-server, waits for them, tears down temp
   651	    dirs.
   652	
   653	## Migration from 8a
   654	
   655	- `eden-wire.server.make_app(store)` → `make_app(store, *,
   656	  shared_token=None)`. Default `None` preserves existing call sites.
   657	- `eden-wire.client.StoreClient(base_url, experiment_id)` →
   658	  `StoreClient(base_url, experiment_id, *, token=None)`. Default
   659	  `None` preserves existing call sites.
   660	- `eden_dispatch.run_experiment` keeps its signature; internally

